	uucp - UNIX To UNIX Communications Menu
		@(#)uucp.sh	1.1 87/03/09

	This menu is a collection of tools used in communicating 
	   between UNIX systems.

	The tools contained in this menu allow the user to:
		* Login into a system from a remote terminal
		  or computer.
		* To call and login to other computers.
		* Copy files to and from remote computers.
		* Execute remote commands, such as "mail".		

